Empty Character Privacy Policy

The application in the previous versions collected some anonymous analytics regarding how many users installed the app and how many users opened the app but keeping all this data anonymous. From Version 2.0.1 or later, the app stopped collecting any data, and now it is powered by the AI2 Engine setup to don't collect data.

Also, this page does not collect any data, and it is currently hosted in the Google Cloud infrastructure
